{
  "stem": "15115.6",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that's-- that's as far as I'm-- as far as Canada is concerned, I am very happy to be alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why I survive?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luck, age-- age, luck, and a little bit of [NON-ENGLISH], a little bit of brains, that I-- I didn't give up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't give up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't say-- because a lot of people give up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went to the electric wire, touched it, and they got burned themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I said, tomorrow's another day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't give up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always hold myself to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's why I survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on top of that, as I told you before, I did not work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- I only work very short times, only in transits when we were moving from one camp to the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a hard times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as soon as I got established in a camp, I was-- I always manage to have a good job, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the job and the food meant survival, because I never got sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was one day in the-- the only thing I used to having in the [INAUDIBLE], in camp, was some boils used to come in, or [NON-ENGLISH], which is this-- you get from the lice, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like you scratch yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you put something on it, it goes away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only thing I had in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a lot of people had many, many sickness, they developed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't, which I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, it's luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Luck, it meant a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
